sentences.english: Did you see that sign back there? I think this is a one way street.
sentences.chinese: 你看到後面那個標誌了嗎？我覺得這是一條單行線。

sentences.english: I'm afraid not. That street is one-way.
sentences.chinese: 恐怕不行，那條街是單行線。

sentences.english: A route is a sequence of one-way streets connecting two intersections.
sentences.chinese: 一條路徑由一系列將兩個路口連通的單行線組成。
